Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_sdf_assertions(25.10)                        reset_sdf_assertions(25.10)

Name
       reset_sdf_assertions

Syntax
       reset_sdf_assertions

       Resets  the  SDF  delays to the values defined in the library. When you
       perform timing analysis, the software uses the SDF values defined  with
       the read_sdf command.

       You can use this command to discard the delay values specified with the
       SDF files, and use the delays defined in the library.

       Note:  You do not need to read in the SDF delays every time you perform
       delay calculations. The software uses the SDF files  specified  earlier
       in the flow.

Parameter
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

Related Information
              * read_sdf

